Introduction

Tsukiashi Amane (아마네 츠키아시) is a Japanese singer under ASOBISYSTEM, member of the idol group FRUITS ZIPPER. She was a member of HKT48's Team TII and graduated on March 30, 2020. She was a contestant on Produce 48.
